Being a feminist means you want equality and that both women and men should be treated equally. Being a *real* feminist means you do not want to see men treated as the inferior sex or any other half of humanity. The fact that people are now of the idea that being a feminist must mean these negative and false things is worrying. It feels as though this once very respected and well thought of movement and all it's accomplishments are being flushed away due to the extremists.

A movement that is supposed to be about equality has extremists who have made it a laughing stock, and it's a sign that this movement has been so strongly dismissed that it has lost all it's accomplishments.
